#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Of course the command for speaking texts is dependent on which speech "
#| "synthesizer you use. Please look into the documentation of your speech "
#| "synthesizer for the command for speaking texts. You can find examples for "
#| "the command in the <link linkend=\"tts\">appendix</link>."
